    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img class="right" src="https://ax5joa.blu.livefilestore.com/y1pghugMbPxX--48legMxXogoiRKbM5iJGhPwlKDzWbhtdtaHuGRwxWaMLl3MVq4iMOCrNLZKJDQLyMCP38msVLf6e7y_RgUaeK/WP_000248.jpg?psid=1" width="200" height="800"></p>

<h2>Ingredient</h2>

<ul>
<li>primary

<ul>
<li>3-4 Kg Cabbage</li>
<li>5 g salt/Kg cabbage</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>salt water

<ul>
<li>1 L water</li>
<li>15 g salt</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>


<h2>Steps</h2>

<ul>
<li>Boil salt &amp; water, let cool</li>
<li>Shred cabbage</li>
<li>Mix salt and cabbage</li>
<li>Pack tightly into crock</li>
<li>Place stones</li>
<li>Cover w/ salt water if required</li>
<li>Cover w/ container and fill channel w/ salt water</li>
<li>Wait 3-6 weeks</li>
</ul>

